    <item>
      <title>瑞士宝盛股价暴跌，因利润下降预示 Benko 复苏艰难</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/julius-baer-sees-client-inflows-accelerate-amid-benko-clean-up</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞士宝盛集团有限公司 (Julius Baer Group Ltd.) 宣布今年上半年利润下降 15%，这表明在该行等待新任首席执行官之际，该行从去年的 Signa 丑闻中复苏的势头可能仍不均衡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/julius-baer-sees-client-inflows-accelerate-amid-benko-clean-up</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 05:22:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国兴业银行和美国银行表示挪威克朗跌势过猛，应买入该货币</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/socgen-bofa-say-time-to-buy-norway-s-krone-as-rout-is-overdone</link>
      <description><![CDATA[挪威克朗已跌至一年多以来的最低点，货币策略师和投资者纷纷抓住这一机会，押注该货币将从底部附近反弹，跃升至十国集团 (G10) 的榜首。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/socgen-bofa-say-time-to-buy-norway-s-krone-as-rout-is-overdone</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
